程序包 Entity

package Entity
  • 类
    类
    说明
    Account
    The Account class represents a bank account with basic functionalities such as deposit, withdraw, and interest rate management.
    AccountManager
    The AccountManager class manages multiple accounts, both current and saving accounts, and handles various operations such as deposits, withdrawals, transfers, and balance inquiries.
    Agent
    The Agent class represents an assistant that helps users manage their bank accounts.
    CurrentAccount
    The CurrentAccount class represents a type of bank account that does not earn interest.
    HistoryTransaction
    The HistoryTransaction class represents a transaction history entry with details such as source, destination, amount, and date of the transaction.
    HistoryTransactionList
    The HistoryTransactionList class manages a list of HistoryTransaction objects, providing methods to add transactions, retrieve transactions, and calculate financial summaries such as total income, expenses, and balance.
    Kids
    The Kids class represents a user entity with various lists and managers for handling accounts, products, tasks, transactions, and messages.
    Message
    The Message class represents a message with a sender, timestamp, and content.
    MessageList
    The MessageList class represents a list of messages associated with a kid.
    Product
    Represents a product with a name and a price.
    ProductList
    Represents a list of products with functionalities to add, remove, and retrieve products.
    SavingAccount
    The SavingAccount class represents a type of bank account that earns interest over a specified period.
    Task
    The Task class represents a task with various properties such as name, reward, state, description, and destination.
    TaskList
    The TaskList class represents a list of tasks and provides various methods to manage the tasks.
